* Thom Donovan American musician/songwriter 
* Shandi Finnessey Miss USA 2004 
* DeDe Dorsey former American football player for the Detroit Lions
* Brian Schaefering former American football player, most notably for the Cleveland Browns
* Alexander Wright former American football player for the Dallas Cowboys, Los Angeles Raiders, and the St. Louis Rams 
* Nicole Hensley women&#x27;s ice hockey goalkeeper for the United States women&#x27;s national ice hockey team
* Pierre Desir American football player most notable for the Indianapolis Colts 
* Daniel Walcott professional hockey player for the Tampa Bay Lightning
* Andrew Koenig member of the Missouri Senate 
* Gary W. Schenkel Executive Director of Chicago&#x27;s Office of Emergency Management and Communications 
* Esmeralda Johnson member of the Saba Island Council
* John Salter American mixed martial artist in Bellator
* Marjorie Finlay American television personality and grandmother of Taylor Swift
* Priyadharshan Kannappan Indian Chess GrandMaster and founder of Chess Gaja Private Limited

