* {{cite web|author = Poole, Steven |author-link=Steven Poole | date = 3 October 1996 | title = Virtually in Love | work = TheGuardian.com | url = https://www.theguardian.com/books/1996/oct/03/sciencefictionfantasyandhorror | access-date= 8 August 2024}} A comprehensive piece by a longstanding reviewer at this British newspaper, that covers the trilogy about a decade after its appearance.

