<doc id="349953" wikidata="Q6876284" url="?curid=349953" title="Miss Canada International">
<text>Miss Canada International &amp; Miss Teen Canada International is a scholarship program for women in Canada. It was founded in 1995 and also has founded in 2005 &quot;The Teddy Bears of Hope Campaign&quot; in 2005 now &quot;A Not For Profit Foundation&quot; run by a board of directors. Miss Canada International and Miss Teen Canada International was purchased by GND Productions Corp.in 2012.
Miss Canada International Inc. held the rights to send a Canadian representative to Miss World from 1997 to 2002.

